<header class="relative pt-40 pb-24 sm:pt-48 sm:pb-36 px-6 sm:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-[600px] pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-10 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-amber-500/[0.05] blur-[140px] animate-float" />
    <div class="absolute top-48 right-1/3 w-72 h-72 rounded-full bg-amber-500/[0.03] blur-[120px] animate-float-delayed" />
    <div class="absolute top-32 right-1/4 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/[0.015] blur-[100px] animate-float-slow" />
  </div>

  <div class="absolute -top-40 right-0 w-[800px] h-[800px] pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-500/[0.08] via-transparent to-transparent blur-[150px]"
      style="animation: spotlight-sweep 20s linear infinite; transform-origin: center" />
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16 lg:gap-20">
    <div class="flex-1 text-center lg:text-left">
      <div class="mb-8 border-l-[3px] border-amber-400 pl-4 max-w-lg animate-fade-in-up">
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 italic leading-relaxed font-display font-normal">
          Right now, someone&rsquo;s calling your salon. You&rsquo;re with a client.
          It rings out. They book somewhere else. This happens 12&ndash;16 times a week.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-[48px] sm:text-[64px] lg:text-[72px] text-white tracking-[-0.03em] leading-[1.1] mb-8 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 50ms">
        That&rsquo;s the last time
        <br />
        <span class="text-amber-400">it happens.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 mb-12 max-w-lg mx-auto lg:mx-0 leading-[1.7] animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 100ms">
        An AI that books appointments, answers questions, and follows up &mdash;
        while you do the work you actually love.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center lg:justify-start gap-6 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 150ms">
        <button
          onclick="window.dispatchEvent(new Event('open-chat-widget'))"
          class="group relative w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-4 bg-amber-400 text-black font-bold text-base rounded-lg tracking-[0.08em] uppercase hover:bg-amber-300 transition-all duration-300 btn-primary-glow cursor-pointer overflow-hidden"
        >
          <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent -translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-full transition-transform duration-700" />
          <span class="relative">See it in action</span>
        </button>
        <a href="https://tally.so/r/1AMoR1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors duration-300">
          Book a demo &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 max-w-md lg:max-w-lg relative w-full animate-fade-in-up group" style="animation-delay: 200ms">
      <div class="absolute -inset-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500/20 via-amber-500/10 to-amber-500/20 rounded-4xl blur-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 -z-10" />

      <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-white/[0.06] shadow-2xl shadow-black/60 group-hover:shadow-black/80 transition-all duration-500">
        <video
          autoplay
          loop
          muted
          playsinline
          class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
          poster="/hero-video-poster.png"
        >
          <source src="/hero-video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>

        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/30 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
